flowchart TD
    Req([Request Arrives at System]) --> Extract[Extract SessionToken]
    Extract --> ValToken{Is SessionToken Valid?}
    
    ValToken -- Yes --> QueryAcc[Query UserAccount for Assigned Role]
    ValToken -- No --> Denied[Deny Access / 401 Unauthorized]
    
    QueryAcc --> QueryRole[Query Role for Permissions]
    QueryRole --> MapPerm[Map Permission against requested SystemModule]
    
    MapPerm --> Eval{Does Permission match Action?}
    
    Eval -- Yes --> Allowed[Allow Access / Execute Action]
    Eval -- No --> Denied[Deny Access / 403 Forbidden]
    
    Allowed --> Log[Log Audit Trail to DBMS]
    Denied --> Log
    
    Log --> End([End Workflow])